Text: @YouthKiAwaaz We are committed to enhancing road & ride safety for driver-partners & commuters alike. Through #StreetSafe we have partnered with stakeholders across the mobility ecosystem, including local authorities & experts to impact safety on a large scale.
Name: Ola

Text: @YouthKiAwaaz Under #StreetSafe, we conduct regular trainings for driver-partners on topics such as Defensive Driving and First Responder, reiterating the importance safety for all.  #SaferRoadsForYou
Name: Ola

Text: @YouthKiAwaaz We also closely monitor our in-app customer feedback section. Driver-partners with perfect track records on road safety are nominated as "Road Safety Brand Ambassadors" setting a positive example for others #SaferRoadsForYou
Name: Ola

Text: @YouthKiAwaaz As for negative feedback, we  reach out to the concerned driver-partner, investigate the case and accordingly provide solutions in the form of re-trainings and official warnings. In severe cases or if repeated complaints are received, their access to the app is also revoked.
Name: Ola

Text: @YouthKiAwaaz During driver-partner on-boarding, we emphasise the need for adequate rest while driving on the platform. Tips like ensuring sufficient sleep, stopping every few hours for rest & driving only during the time when they are normally awake are shared regularly. #SaferRoadsforYou
Name: Ola

Text: @YouthKiAwaaz To strengthen the safety of commuters, we have pioneered key safety features that include : 1. Emergency button - Tapping the button enables an immediate telephonic call from a dedicated quick response team, specialised in handling safety queries contd.
Name: Ola

Text: @YouthKiAwaaz 2. Share details -This feature enables our commuters to share details with their loved ones, about their driver and vehicle along with the vehicle permit number. Their ride can also be tracked by their friends with the help of our live GPS tracking system.  Contd.
Name: Ola

Text: @YouthKiAwaaz We also have Ola Guardian - A real-time monitoring system that tracks on-going trips by keeping a tab on ride indicators such as route deviations, and unexpected stops. Our Safety Response Team then assesses this data and contacts the customer to provide necessary assistance.
Name: Ola

Text: @YouthKiAwaaz This was fun! Keep up the conversation.  #SaferRoadsForYou
Name: Ola
